quran[5{c,v,t}:
9,118,"aur unn tenu ko bhi is ne maaf kya jin ke maamla ko multawi kar diya gaya tha jab zameen apni saari wusat ke bawajood un par tang ho gayi aur un ki apni jaanen bhi un par baar honay lagen aur unhon ne jaan liya ke Allah se bachney ke liye koi jaye panah khud Allah hi ke daman rehmat ke siwa nahi hai, to Allah apni meharbani se un ki taraf palta taakay woh is ki taraf palat ayen, yaqeenan woh bara maaf karne wala aur Raheem hai"
9,119,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, Allah se daro aur sachey logon ka sath do"
9,120,"madeeney ke bashindon aur gird o nawah ke badwiyonko yeh hargiz zaiba nah tha ke Allah ke rasool ko chore kar ghar baith rehtay aur is ki taraf se be parwa ho kar apne apne nafs ki fikar mein lag jatay is liye ke aisa kabhi nah hoga ke Allah ki raah mein bhook pyaas aur jismani mushaqqat ki koi takleef woh jhelen, aur munkareen haq ko jo raah nagawaar hai uss par koi qadam woh utthayen, aur kisi dushman se ( adawat haq ka ) ka koi intiqam woh len aur is ke badlay un ke haq mein aik amal Saleh nah likha jaye yaqeenan Allah ke haan mohsinon ka haq alkhdmt mara nahi jata hai"
9,121,isi terhan yeh bhi kabhi nah hoga ke ( raah khuda mein ) thora ya bohat koi kharch woh utthayen aur ( sae jehaad mein ) koi waadi woh paar karen aur un ke haq mein usay likh nah liya jaye taakay Allah un ke is achay karname ka sila inhen ataa kere
9,122,"aur yeh kuch zurori nah tha ke ahal imaan saaray ke saaray hi nikal kharray hotay, magar aisa kyun nah howa ke un ki abadi ke har hissa mein se kuch log nikal kar atay aur deen ki samajh peda karte aur wapas ja kar apne ilaqay ke bashindon ko khabardaar karte taakay woh ( ghair musalmana rawish se ) parhaiz karte"
